Devfolio is a community-driven platform based in Bengaluru, India, designed to empower developers by simplifying participation in and organization of hackathons. Since hosting its first community hackathon in January 2019, Devfolio has grown into a powerhouse for fostering innovation, collaboration, and skill development. With a mission to bridge the gap between talent and opportunity, Devfolio has supported over 1,300 hackathons worldwide, bringing more than 75,000 ideas to life. Its Builders page is a testament to this mission, spotlighting the individuals who embody the spirit of creation and problem-solving.

